同偕到老不靠運氣"},{"pid":"bcf7d7e358fecb06d1457299ab3c71304d4fefde","tid":988254,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec7b29aba96a1ad4bf705d9813cb4554d963738","tid":988254,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:17:07.000Z","msg":"今天高汁"},{"pid":"3e7133841f280571bbbabc28e28ebdd4112d8a82","tid":988254,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ec7b29aba96a1ad4bf705d9813cb4554d963738","tid":988254,"uid":138232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:17:07.000Z","msg":"今天高汁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:17:57.000Z","msg":"咁偷巴就幫手作下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1001f9dfe7b57eab7dd4542a435a2c32982c6f","tid":988254,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"太臭好似無咩人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fe11459aeffaf9b30846efbd3eadb75a3aa2bf","tid":988254,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"踏著大便都分享  <br />\n日日大便也沒抆屎~脫腸<br />\n食住大便都分享  <br />\n就<span style=\"color: red;\">用大便</span>發掘 好~衰相<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">就在糞便</span><br />\n睇吓會唔會順口啲...連續三句都大便...好似好咩咁..."},{"pid":"88cf2ea5ffb56b3c576901580ea3fccedc060907","tid":988254,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9fe11459aeffaf9b30846efbd3eadb75a3aa2bf","tid":988254,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"踏著大便都分享  <br />\n日日大便也沒抆屎~脫腸<br />\n食住大便都分享  <br />\n就<span style=\"color: red;\">用大便</span>發掘 好~衰相<